## Troubleshooting

### CORS Errors
- Ensure `FRONTEND_URL` is set correctly in backend env vars
- Check that frontend URL matches exactly (no trailing slash)

### MongoDB Connection Failed
- Verify IP whitelist in MongoDB Atlas
- Check connection string format
- Ensure database user has correct permissions

### JWT Errors
- Make sure `JWT_SECRET` is set and consistent
- Clear browser localStorage and re-login

### Static Files Not Loading
- Ensure HTML files are in the correct directory
- Check that your hosting platform serves static files
- Verify file paths in HTML (use relative paths)

